name: 🏴 Babylon Falling 🏴 looping animation
description:
Follow the money and you will see that 1% of a country’s population owns most of the wealth and assets. This capital represents a major force, only interested in protecting the power structure in place.

It is about time that these power structures are brought down and with it the old-world institutions that have benefited from colonialism, slave trade and war for centuries. Babylon is falling. We are legion.
